{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Uses \b sparse spatial partitioning \b0 for increased optimization.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Capable of simulating \b tens of thousands of agents at 60+ fps easily \b0 on most modern processors.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Capable of creating highly complex simulations, includes a Predator vs. Prey example scene.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Includes \b physics-based obstacle avoidance\b0 . So your swarms won't end up flying through walls!\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Comes with classic boid behaviours such as seperation, alignment, cohesion; but also comes with more such as target, obstacle, avoidance, hover, gravity, and more! You can mix and match to easily create your own swarms, \b no coding required\b0 !\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Built to be as \b simple to extend \b0 as possible so you can easily \b create your own behaviours\b0 !\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Tons of customizable features to finely tune your swarms to exactly your needs.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Includes extensive web-based documentation and video tutorial.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b Full source code included\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Includes 3 examples scenes: Birds, Fish, PredatorPrey\par

